name: On a Mission to have a good time - T-Shirt
description:
Proudly screen printed by hand in London, limited edition of 30 made.
Super sharp blend of two colors using single silk screen, very difficult technique!

Printed on preshrunk Premium Heavyweight T-shirts. 100% cotton, 200 gsm weight. Carefully stitched with 100% cotton GOOD TIMES labels.

Inspiration for these is the 1970's custom chopper scene, DIY rebel culture and 70's screen printing techniques and use of colors.

Visit my blog http://onamissiontohaveagoodtime.tumblr.com/

--------------------------------------------------

For longer lasting quality:

Wash in COLD water
Do not TUMBLE DRY 
Warm IRON on reverse.

--------------------------------------------------

Due to the printing technique, color fade might slightly differ from a t-shirt to another. These are carefully selected, so they all exceed selling standards.

name: On a mission to have a good time
description:
A limited series of A2 screen printed posters realized with a 2 color blend.

Inspiration for these is the 1970's custom chopper scene, DIY rebel culture 
and 70's screen printing techniques and use of colors.

Posters are printed on white paper, all of them are a blend of 2 colors.
The series counds 25 posters for each design. Every poster is slightly different by the other due to the hand blending technique used.

*Colors might appear slightly different by the picture on this shop.
